## API (mismo contrato que v1)

### POST /analyze

```json
// Request
{
    "call_id": "call-123",
    "audio_base64": "<PCM 16-bit en base64>",
    "sample_rate": 8000
}

// Response
{
    "call_id": "call-123",
    "result": "HUMAN",          // o "MACHINE"
    "confidence": 0.9234,
    "reason": "Resemblyzer+SVM: HUMAN con 92% de confianza",
    "forced": false,
    "voice_seconds": 1.24,
    "total_seconds": 1.50
}
```

### WebSocket /ws/{call_id}

```
Cliente conecta → envía chunks binarios PCM → recibe JSON con decisión
```

### WebSocket /ws/stream

```
Cliente conecta → envía JSON config → recibe "ready" → envía chunks → recibe decisión
```

### GET /health

```json
{
    "status": "healthy",
    "model_loaded": true,
    "svm_ready": true,
    "active_sessions": 5,
    "analyses_in_progress": 3,
    "thread_pool_max_workers": 8
}
```

